Marketing Supervisor
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/01 11:27:19
Ref. JB3046275
Job Description
Our client a multinational manufacturing company – FORTUNE 500 is seeking to hire a Marketing Supervisor.
This is a Contract Staffing role under Manpower for a period of 9 months and renewable depending on business needs and/or individual performance.
Your duties will include:
•	Support Strategy Development
•	Support Commercial Plan Development
•	Lead Commercial Plant Deployment
•	Responsible for/control Marketing budget
•	Handle agency briefings/Consumer Engagement deployment/settings KPIs and tracking
•	Handle regional Product and Packaging development projects
•	Accountable for timely delivery of approved initiatives
Support sales team with development of Trade marketing programs
•	Accountable for compliance, implementation and training of the Marketing Code. Ensuring all materials are approved by Legal and internal stakeholders.
Skills
Candidate Profile:
- Fluency in English is a MUST.
- Fluency in French, Arabic & Hindi a PLUS.
- Flexibility on schedule is a MUST.
- Very flexible and open to travel.
